title: Bishop Moore Senior Apartments / Low Income Move In Today
posting_body: ['Bishop Moore is a community for seniors 62 and over, offering independent living in a beautiful newly renovated building within the community of Highland Park.', 'Rent based on income.', 'Relax in one of our many 1 bedroom apartments with spacious floor plans designed to offer the most comfort for day to day affordable living.', 'Amenities:', 'Free Heat/Water', 'Handicap Accessible', 'Controlled Access', 'Intercom System', 'On-site Laundry Facilities', '24 Hour Maintenance', 'Caring and Friendly Staff', 'Close to Shopping', 'Community/Game Room with TV & Kitchenette', 'Accessible to all Major Freeways', 'Please stop by our leasing office at 99 Manchester Pkwy, Highland Park, MI 48203.', 'Our office is open Monday-Friday 8:00am-5:00pm.', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY']
